package com.graphs.exceptions.vertex
Vertex-related exceptions package.
Since:
1.1
  • Exceptions
    Class
    Description
    NegativeVertexIndexException
    This exception can be thrown whenever negative vertex index occurs.
    NoSuchVertexIndexException
    This exception can be thrown whenever a graph does not contain a vertex with a given index.
    VertexIndexException
    This is an abstract exception class related to any vertex index problem.
